data.name: minDeltaDataGridViewTextBoxColumn.ToolTipText
data.value: The minimum TotalDelta% permissible before we must adjust the portfolio. If we have fewer than 9 days to expiration, we raise the minimum minute-by-minute linearly so that we reach 1/3 of the way to the target by expiration

data.name: maxDeltaDataGridViewTextBoxColumn.ToolTipText
data.value: The maximum TotalDelta% permissible before we must adjust the portfolio. If we have fewer than 9 days to expiration, we lower the maximum minute-by-minute linearly so that we reach 1/3 of the way to the target by expiration
